### Summary

Issue #695 requires showing context pills (currently mobile-only via `md:hidden`) on desktop too. The fix adds a `hidden md:flex flex-wrap` desktop pills row inside the existing input area div, between the textarea container and the keyboard-hint text — matching the "Relevance Chips" pattern from the design file. Mobile pills are untouched.

