| Field | Value |
|-------|-------|
| Complexity | LOW |
| Files to UPDATE | 1 (`ChatPanel.tsx`) |
| Files to REGENERATE | Screenshots in `frontend/e2e/visual.spec.ts-snapshots/` |
| Total Tasks | 2 |

### Key Patterns Discovered

- `activeContextThings` computed at `ChatPanel.tsx:761-777` — already in scope, no logic changes needed
- Mobile pill button at `ChatPanel.tsx:897-904` — exact pattern to mirror for desktop pills
- Insert point: after `</div>` closing textarea container (~line 1060), before `<p>` keyboard hint (line 1061)

### UX Transformation

- **BEFORE**: Desktop input area has no pill display; `activeContextThings` computed but invisible on desktop
- **AFTER**: Desktop shows wrapping row of clickable context pills below the textarea, styled as "Relevance Chips"

### Risks

- Wrong insert location causes JSX parse error: mitigated by reading lines 1005-1064 before editing and validating with `npm run type-check`

### Confidence Score

**9/10** — display-only change in a single well-understood file, insert location is precise, all values already in scope, one JSX block to add.
